Da, to joj je pravo ime.

168
00:16:07,330 --> 00:16:09,470
Janine, ne smeš da ujedaš ljude.

169
00:16:13,036 --> 00:16:15,036
Mogu da ti kažem tajnu?

170
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:19,240
Da.

171
00:16:20,778 --> 00:16:23,208
Mogu da radim šta god hoću.

172
00:16:29,687 --> 00:16:31,687
Mogu.

173
00:16:33,190 --> 00:16:36,130
Rodila sam bebu! I to zdravu.

174
00:16:36,193 --> 00:16:38,403
Zdravu bebu!

175
00:16:38,461 --> 00:16:40,561
