183
00:17:10,127 --> 00:17:12,127
Ok.

184
00:17:12,763 --> 00:17:14,763
Ok.

185
00:17:18,636 --> 00:17:20,202
On...

186
00:17:20,203 --> 00:17:23,343
On me voli.

187
00:17:23,406 --> 00:17:25,736
On me voli najviše.

188
00:17:28,746 --> 00:17:30,746
Ko?

189
00:17:30,914 --> 00:17:33,654
On. Moj Zapovednik.

190
00:17:36,219 --> 00:17:38,219
Voli te? -Da!

191
00:17:39,456 --> 00:17:42,986
Voli mene i voli Charlotte.

192
00:17:43,060 --> 00:17:45,060
I mi ćemo...

193
00:17:46,096 --> 00:17:49,326
Pobećićemo zajedno.

194
00:17:58,075 --> 00:18:00,075
To ti je on rekao?

195
00:18:02,479 --> 00:18:04,519
Ne moraš da mi veruješ.

196
00:18:05,983 --> 00:18:08,753
Ali on mene voli.

197
00:18:13,757 --> 00:18:15,757
I mi ćemo...

198
00:18:17,695 --> 00:18:19,755
Bićemo porodica.

199
00:18:26,036 --> 00:18:28,236
Sladoled! 'Ajde!

200
00:18:58,602 --> 00:19:01,002
Auto stiže, gđo. -Hvala, sačekaćemo.

201
00:19:08,145 --> 00:19:10,145
Je l' ti bilo zabavno?

202
00:19:12,082 --> 00:19:14,082
Da.

203
00:19:14,351 --> 00:19:16,421
Hvala.

204
00:19:16,487 --> 00:19:18,687
Jesi posetila prijateljicu?

205
00:19:20,323 --> 00:19:23,989
